{"title":"Kehakoorija","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"peony-body-scrub-with-organic-fruit-oils-250-ml","title":"Magrada Peony Body Scrub With Organic Fruit Oils 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg height=\"100\" width=\"100\" alt=\"pure beauty global awards 2019 finalist\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/17-1-300x300.png\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11711\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe efficient sea salt and fruit oil composition captivates with a Mediterranean elegance. The mineral-rich finely ground sea salt gently peels off dead skin cells. Apricot, safflower, and jojoba oils, however, nurture and soften the skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePeeling the body helps to invigorate the skin regeneration process and improves subcutaneous circulation. This is a luxurious beauty treatment which tones and moisturises, making the skin beautifully radiant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCold-pressed organic safflower oil\u003c\/span\u003e restores and preserves the moisture level of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic apricot kernel oil\u003c\/span\u003e with its light structure nurtures the skin with minerals and vitamins A, B, C, and E.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic jojoba oil\u003c\/span\u003e contains vitamins A and E and has wonderful tightening properties.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic black elderflower berry extract\u003c\/span\u003e calms irritated skin, while the aroma of the berries adds alluring notes to the scent of the fruit oil.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe body scrub contains finely ground sea salt, which still has all of its biologically active minerals. The sea salt helps to relax muscles and stimulates the natural regeneration process of skin cells.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe peony aroma\u003c\/span\u003e comes from natural petals of the flower and has been captured into the bottle in France. The alluring flower oil is custom-made.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eRub the body scrub on moist skin with circular movements and rinse with water. We advise to use the scrub once or twice a week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Sodium Chloride, Glycerin, Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Seed Oil*, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil*, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil*, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Parfum (Natural), Magnesium Aluminum Silicate, Kaolin, Montmorillonite, Mica\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 100%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e | alcohol-free |cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927702024519,"sku":"","price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-peony-body-scrub-with-organic-fruit-oils-250ml-2310111.png?v=1763665704"},{"product_id":"lavender-body-scrub-with-grapefruit-essential-oil-250-ml","title":"Magrada Lavender Body Scrub With Grapefruit Essential Oil 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11691\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/auhinnad-300x300.png\" alt=\"anne stiil ilulemmik 2017\" width=\"99\" height=\"99\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe nightly beauty ritual will create a spa-like pleasure in the comfort of your home. The organic body oil will provide a relaxing pleasure for your body and senses. The composition of the naturally extracted essential oils from small organic producers alleviates tensions and facilitates falling asleep.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCold-pressed organic safflower oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003erestores and preserves the moisture level of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic apricot kernel oil\u003c\/span\u003e with its light structure nurtures the skin with minerals and vitamins A, B, C, and E.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic jojoba oil\u003c\/span\u003e contains vitamins A and E and has wonderful tightening properties.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAromatherapy has a positive effect on your well-being and senses. Grapefruit oil is calming and relaxing, improves your mood, alleviates anxiety, and promotes sleep.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProvence – one of the most beautiful areas of France with violet lavender fields which only give the best organic lavender essential oil.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCold-pressed organic white grapefruit essential oil adds sunny synergy.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOrganic juniper essential oil has a relaxing and calming effect.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eRub the body scrub on moist skin with circular movements and rinse with water. We advise to use the scrub once or twice a week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Sodium Chloride, Glycerin, Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Seed Oil*, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil*, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil*, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Citrus Paradisi (Grapefruit) Peel Oil*, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Oil*, Juniperus Communis (Juniper) Fruit Oil, Linalool, Limonene\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Default\"\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Default\"\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 100%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Default\"\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927726240071,"sku":"","price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-lavender-body-scrub-with-grapefruit-essential-oil-250ml-906916.jpg?v=1739897402"},{"product_id":"body-scrub-bali-spa","title":"HOIA Body Scrub Bali Spa 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBali Spa Body Scrub is inspired by the sensual scents of Bali, which are known to enrich your love life, calm your mind and body. This body scrub is designed to create an ultimate spa-experience at your own home –therapeutic essential oils filling your bathroom with sensual aroma… invigorating sugarmassage while scrubbing, that silky-soft skin after you are finished… It makes you feel that you just stepped out of your favorite spa! Deliciously smelling body scrub cleans, tones and while applying massages your skin, it removes dead skin cells and helps to alleviate dry and flaky skin. It is rich in organic unrefined shea butter and coconut oil, which leave your skin soft and silky smooth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply on moist skin and massage for a few minutes, then rinse with water. No need to use a moisturizer afterwards. Do not use this scrub right before tanning or solarium. Keep the product under +25 °C.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e *Sucrose, *Butyrospermum Parkii  Butter, *Cocos Nucifera Oil, Plumeria Alba Flower Oil, Citrus Aurantifolia Peel Oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Tocopherol, **Citral, **Citronellol, **Eugenol, **Coumarin, **Geraniol, **Linalool, **Limonene, **Hydroxycitronellal, **Benzyl Alcohol, **Benzyl Salicylate. * From Organic Farming. ** Natural components of essential oils.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48932042572103,"sku":"","price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-body-scrub-bali-spa-200ml-191051.jpg?v=1739897408"},{"product_id":"body-scrub-coffee-peppermint","title":"HOIA Body Scrub Coffee \u0026 Peppermint 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eExtremely invigorating coffee scrub cleans, tones and massages your skin, it removes dead skin cells and helps to alleviate dry and flaky skin. It is rich in unrefined organic shea butter and coconut oil, which leaves your skin soft, moisturized and silky smooth. Fresh ground coffee beans have a high caffeine content, which is known to help prevent cellulite. Peppermint essential oil is refreshing, uplifting and invigorating.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply on moist skin and massage on your skin for a few minutes, then rinse with water. No need to use a moisturizer afterwards. Keep the product under +25 °C.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e *Sucrose, Coffee Arabica Beans, *Butyrospermun Parkii Butter, *Cocos Nucifera Oil, *Mentha Piperita  Leaf Oil, Tocopherol,**Limonene.  *From organic farming.  **Natural component of essential oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48932042998087,"sku":"","price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-body-scrub-coffee-peppermint-200ml-813070.jpg?v=1739897403"},{"product_id":"body-scrub-lemongrass","title":"HOIA Body Scrub Lemongrass 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eZestfully smelling lemongrass body scrub cleans, tones and massages your skin, removes dead skin cells and helps to alleviate dry, red and aky skin. It is rich in unrefined organic shea butter and coconut oil, which leaves your skin soft, moisturized and silky smooth. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply on moist skin and massage on your skin for few minutes, rinse with water. No need to use a moisturizer afterwards. Keep product under +25 °C.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e *Sucrose,*Butyrospermum Parkii  Butter, *Cocos Nucifera  Oil, Cymbopogon Flexuosus Herb  Oil, ­**Citral, *Gerniol, **Linalool, **Cintronellol, **Limonene. * From Organic Farming. ** Natural components of essential oils.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48932068360519,"sku":"","price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-body-scrub-lemongrass-200ml-783431.jpg?v=1739897402"},{"product_id":"hoia-shimmer-scrub-200ml","title":"HOIA Shimmer Body Scrub Überblingen 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eÜberblingen is a super shimmering body scrub with a tropical mandarin and flower (ylang-ylang) aroma. Shimmer Scrub is rich in organic unrefined shea butter and coconut oil, which effectively moisturize, hydrate and soften your skin; it contains sugar and Himalayan salt, which help to scrub away all impurities and dead skin cells leaving your skin soft and silky smooth. There is no need to use a moisturizer after using this scrub. Shimmering particles in this product are of mineral origin and they do not harm environment.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply in a circular motion and massage it on your skin for a few minutes, rinse with water. No need to use a moisturizer afterwards. Keep product under +25 °C.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSucrose, Sodium Chloride (Himalayan salt), *Butyrospermum Parkii (shea) Butter, *Cocos Nucifera (coconut) Oil, Citrus Nobilis (mandarin) Peel oil, Cananga Odorata (ylang -ylang) Flower Oil, Elettaria Cardamomum (cardemon) Seed Oil, Mica, **Tin Oxide (CI 77861), **Titanium Oxide (CI 77891), **CI 77491 (Iron Oxide), **Synthetic Fluorphlogopite, ***Linalool, ***Limonene. * From organic farming. ** Plastic-free mineral component of Mica. ***Natural component of essential oil.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49554365874503,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-shimmer-body-scrub-uberblingen-200ml-977319.png?v=1739897255"},{"product_id":"hoia-body-scrub-beach-bum-200ml","title":"HOIA Anti-Cellulite Body Scrub Beach Bum 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Body Scrub is designed to fight cellulite. It is rich in caffeine and powerful essential oils. With scrubbing massage it helps to boost micro circulation, combat fluid retention, detoxify, tone and tighten your skin. This product has a high content of unrefined organic shea butter and coconut oil, which nourishes and moisturizes your skin. Body Scrub improves elasticity, keeps it healthy-looking and silky smooth.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eMassage the scrub on problematic areas for 5 minutes, let it sit for a few minutes and rinse with water, For maximum results use daily. No need to use a moisturizer after your scrubbing session.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Sucrose, *Butyrospermum Parkii butter, *Cocos Nucifera oil, Coee Arabica Bean powder, Sodium Chloride (Himalayan salt), Citrus Paradisi Peel oil, *Rosimarinus Ocinalis Leaf oil, *Cymbopogon Flexuosus Leaf oil, *Juniperus Virginiana oil, Piper Nigrum Fruit oil, Tocopherol, **Linalool, **Geraniol. *From organic farming. **Natural components of essential oils.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49554368364871,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-anti-cellulite-body-scrub-beach-bum-200ml-650540.jpg?v=1739897246"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-body-scrub-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Body Scrub 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic body scrub, specially designed to cleanse and exfoliate the skin gently, to remove dead skin cells and revitalise your body.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), finely ground apricot kernels (exfoliating), wheat germ oil (moisturising), organic extracts of birch leaf (purifying), lavender (soothing) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to damp skin. In circular movement massage in gently. Rinse off thoroughly. On contact with water and by gently massaging in, the scrub transforms into a nourishing lotion that can be washed off easily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Glycerin**, Aqua*, Decyl Glucoside*, Prunus Armeniaca Seed Powder**, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil**, Citric Acid*, Betaine*, Xanthan Gum*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Betula Alba Leaf Extract**, Glycine Soja Seed Extract*, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (74,9%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901064843591,"sku":null,"price":19.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-body-scrub-50ml-231547.webp?v=1739897173"},{"product_id":"hoia-body-scrub-unicorn-dust-200ml","title":"HOIA Body Scrub Unicorn Dust 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUnicorn Dust body scrub is a moisturizing scrub that leaves your skin silky soft and luxuriously sparkling. This scrub is rich in organic unrefined shea butter and coconut oil, which effectively moisturize, hydrate and soften your skin. The scrub contains sugar, which offers your skin a nice and stimulating massage. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUnicorn Dust is enriched with refreshing essential oils, which will add a mood-boosting and pleasant aromatherapic spa experience to your scrubbing session. Shimmering particles in this product are of mineral origin and they do not harm the environment. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply in a circular motion and massage it on your skin for few minutes, rinse with water and enjoy your sparkle. No need to use a moisturizer afterwards. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDo not use the scrub before sunbathing and visiting the solarium.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Sucrose, *Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, *Cocos Nucifera Oil, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus Seed oil, *Lavandula Angustifolia Flower oil, *Mentha Piperita Leaf oil, *Citrus Aurantifolia Peel oil, **Fluorphlogopite, **Titanium Dioxide, **Tin Oxide, ***Limonene, ***Linalool, ***Citral, ***Geraniol. *From organic farming. **Mineral component of Mica. ***Natural components of essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51104589185351,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-body-scrub-unicorn-dust-200ml-403541.jpg?v=1740808676"},{"product_id":"hoia-body-scrub-strawberry-margarita-200ml","title":"HOIA Body Scrub Strawberry Margarita 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStrawberry Margarita is an enticing body scrub with the aroma of strawberries and lemons, transforming your shower into an aromatic exfoliating spa ritual. The product helps stimulate circulation, cools the skin, removes dead skin cells, and leaves the skin delightfully soft and silky.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe body scrub contains organic unrefined shea butter and coconut oil, which effectively alleviate skin dryness and nourish the skin with vitamins.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eMassage the scrub onto the skin in circular motions – start from the soles of your feet and work your way up to the neck. Allow it to work for a few minutes, enjoy the aromatherapy, and then rinse off. There’s no need to moisturize the skin after using the body scrub. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDo not use the scrub before sunbathing and visiting the solarium.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Sucrose, *Cocos Nucifera Oil, *Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, *Citrus Limon Peel Oil, Natural Parfum, Helianthus Annuus Seed oil, Tocopherol, **Limonene, **Linalool. * From Organic Farming. ** Natural component of essential oil.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51104615465287,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-body-scrub-strawberry-margarita-200ml-410886.jpg?v=1740808676"},{"product_id":"hoia-body-scrub-virgin-mojito-200ml","title":"HOIA Body Scrub Virgin Mojito 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis citrusy fresh Mojito-scented body scrub transforms your shower and sauna experiences into aromatic exfoliating spa rituals. The scrub helps stimulate circulation, cools the skin, aids in removing dead skin cells, and leaves the skin delightfully soft and silky.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eContaining organic unrefined Nilotica shea butter and coconut oil, the scrub effectively alleviates skin dryness and nourishes the skin with vitamins. The fresh scent is imparted by lime and peppermint essential oils.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eMassage the scrub onto the skin in circular motions – start from the soles of your feet and work your way up to the neck. Allow it to work for a few minutes and then rinse off. There’s no need to moisturize afterward.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDo not use the scrub before sunbathing and visiting the solarium.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Sucrose, *Cocos Nucifera Oil, *Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, *Citrus Aurantifolia Peel Oil, *Mentha Piperita Leaf Oil, *Citral, **Limonene, **Linalool. * From Organic Farming. ** Natural component of essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51104630047047,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-body-scrub-virgin-mojito-200ml-768258.jpg?v=1740808668"},{"product_id":"hoia-body-scrub-saltshaker-200ml","title":"HOIA Body Scrub Saltshaker 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSaltshaker Body Scrub is a freshly scented body scrub with Himalayan salt and magnesium, providing your skin with a refreshing and aromatherapeutic spa experience. After use, your skin will be nourished and silky soft. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe body scrub contains organic unrefined shea butter, coconut oil, and aloe extract, which improve skin circulation, relieve dryness, and make the skin silky smooth. The inclusion of magnesium and a carefully selected blend of essential oils helps your body relax and your mind to calm down.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eMassage the scrub onto the skin in circular motions – start from the soles of your feet and work your way up to the neck. Allow it to work for a few minutes and then rinse off. There’s no need to moisturize afterward.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDo not use the scrub before sunbathing and visiting the solarium.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSodium Chloride (Himaalaja sool), Magnesium Sulfate, *Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Cocos Nucifera Oil, *Lavandula Angustifolia Flower oil, *Hyssop Ocinalis Decumbens Leaf oil, *Citrus Bergamia Peel oil, Aloe Vera extract. **Limonene, *Linalool. *Organic. **Natural component of essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51104635519303,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-body-scrub-saltshaker-200ml-566902.png?v=1740808670"},{"product_id":"hoia-body-scrub-sassy-citrus-200ml","title":"HOIA Body Scrub Sassy Citrus 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"60\" data-end=\"366\"\u003eThis deliciously scented Sassy Citrus Body Scrub cleanses, tones, and gently massages the skin while removing dead skin cells and relieving dryness and flakiness. Infused with organic unrefined shea butter and coconut oil, it deeply nourishes, leaving the skin soft, smooth, and hydrated.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"368\" data-end=\"503\"\u003eThe invigorating blend of citrus essential oils provides a refreshing boost, helping to combat fatigue and uplift the senses.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eMassage the scrub onto the skin in circular motions – start from the soles of your feet and work your way up to the neck. Allow it to work for a few minutes and then rinse off. There’s no need to moisturize afterward.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDo not use the scrub before sunbathing and visiting the solarium.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eStore below +25°C\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSucrose, *Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, *Cocos Nucifera Oil, Citrus Grandis Peel Oil, Citrus Aurantifolia Oil, Citrus Aurantium Bergamia Fruit Oil, **Limonene, **Linalool, **Citral. * From Organic Farming. ** Natural components of essential oils.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51104644399431,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-body-scrub-sassy-citrus-200ml-880150.jpg?v=1740808667"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-seabuckthorn-body-scrub-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Seabuckthorn Body Scrub 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNatural Seabuckthorn Body Scrub – your ultimate skincare indulgence for radiant, velvety-soft skin. This body scrub is expertly formulated to provide your skin with the care it truly deserves. Infused with the goodness of sea buckthorn and enriched with exfoliating particles, it offers a multi-dimensional approach to skincare. It gently removes dull, lifeless skin cells, revealing a fresh and luminous complexion. All this without causing any harm to your delicate skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe true beauty lies in moisturizing herbal oils. As you massage the scrub onto your skin, these oils work in harmony to lavish your body with hydration, leaving it irresistibly soft and silky. Zesty essence of orange and mandarin essential oils not only stimulate your skin but also invigorate your mind, transforming your shower routine into an awakening experience that leaves you feeling refreshed and renewed. ECOCERT \/ COSMOS eco-certificate guarantees that this body scrub is crafted with the utmost respect for nature, ensuring that your beauty regimen is as sustainable as it is effective.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEmbrace the luxury of softness, the thrill of rejuvenation, and the enchantment of an energizing citrus symphony – all within a single jar of LUUV Natural Seabuckthorn Body Scrub.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGentle, but effective\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eDoesn\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e‘\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003et dry skin\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRefreshing citrus aroma\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSafe for the environment\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eSeabuckthorn oil\u003c\/span\u003e is a natural super moisturizer. It contains a high concentration of fatty acids, including omega-3, omega-6, omega-7, and omega-9, which help maintain the skin’s moisture level and prevent moisture loss.\u003cbr\u003eThe high content of vitamin C in the oil makes the skin radiant and bright, helping to even out the complexion.\u003cbr\u003eThe antioxidants present in the oil, such as vitamin C, vitamin E, and beta-carotene, protect the skin from free radical damage and promote a youthful appearance.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCarrot oil\u003c\/span\u003e (specifically carrot seed oil) contains a lot of carotene, which gives a complexion-enhancing effect. Carrot oil is always in a carrier oil (i.e., diluted) because it is too intense on its own. It contains a lot of vitamin A. The natural SPF of carrot oil is around 40, but since it is diluted, it ends up around SPF 10.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExfoliating particles made from\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erice\u003c\/span\u003e – no plastic! The particles are not angular or sharp, so they do not damage the skin. At the same time, they are strong enough to provide a good exfoliating effect. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified | paraben free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eIncorporate it into your routine once a week to maintain beautifully polished skin. Also ideal before applying self-tanning products, ensuring an even and flawless tan that lasts.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Powder, Glycerin, Dunaliella Salina Extract, Helianthus Annus Seed Oil, Coco-Glucoside, Glyceryl Oleate, Xanthan gum, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) oil, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Oil, Citrus Nobilis Peel (Mandarin) Oil, Citric Acid, Sodium benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Aroma, Citral, Linalool, Limonene\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115441717575,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-seabuckthorn-body-scrub-200ml-989413.png?v=1740560026"},{"product_id":"nurme-sea-buckthorn-and-orange-sugar-scrub-250g","title":"NURME Sea Buckthorn and Orange Sugar Scrub 250g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRefreshing body scrub with sweet orange, sugar and sea buckthorn oil will give your skin a much needed vitamin load. Sea buckthorn oil is rich in vitamins, promotes skin cell renewal, strengthens it and protects the skin. At the same time, sweet orange essential oil has a stimulating effect and gives energy irresistibly good scent. Suitable for all skin types. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount of scrub in a circular motion on wet skin, gently massage and then rinse. It is not advisable to wash the peeled areas with soap to maximize the oils in the scrub.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Sucrose (Sugar), Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate,  Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Oil, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Sweet Orange) Peel Oil, Sodium Benzoate (and) Potassium Sorbate, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Limonene*\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e* Occurs naturally in essential oils\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52880737632583,"sku":null,"price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-sea-buckthorn-and-orange-sugar-scrub-250g-2757463.webp?v=1765078816"},{"product_id":"nurme-grapefruit-sugar-scrub-250g","title":"NURME Grapefruit Sugar Scrub 250g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRefreshing body scrub with grapefruit, sugar and pink clay will give your skin a much-needed vitamin boost. Pink clay is rich in minerals and iron which improve elasticity while grapefruit is full of vitamin C, leaving your skin firm and smooth and smelling absolutely delicious. Regular use helps reduce the appearance of cellulite. Suitable for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount of scrub on wet skin in circular motions, massage gently and rinse. In order to get maximum results from the oils in the scrub, we do not recommend washing the exfoliated areas with soap.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Sucrose (Sugar), Prunus Amaygdalus Dulcis (Almond Sweet) Oil, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Simmondsia Shinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Citrus Grandis (Grapefruit) Peel Oil, Sodium Benzoate (and) Potassium Sorbate, Kaolin (Pink Clay), Tocopherol (Vitamin E). Limonene*\u003cem\u003e \u003c\/em\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e* Occurs naturally in essential oils\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52880787964231,"sku":null,"price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-grapefruit-sugar-scrub-250g-9359903.webp?v=1765078814"},{"product_id":"nurme-sea-mineral-scrub-250g","title":"NURME Sea Mineral Scrub 250g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDeep cleansing sea mineral scrub will fill your bathroom with delicious fresh peppermint scent. Sea minerals are known for their ability to remove toxins from the body and to improve blood circulation in the skin. The scrub will get rid of dead skin cells and will leave your skin feeling young and fresh. Sea salt combined with refreshing peppermint helps reduce the appearance of cellulite.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount of scrub on wet skin in circular motions. Wait a few minutes before rinsing. In order to get maximum results from the oils in the scrub, we do not recommend washing the exfoliated areas with soap.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Maris Sal (Sea salt), Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Simmondsia Shinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Mentha Piperita (Peppermint) Oil, Sodium Benzoate, Mentha Viridis (Spearmint) Leaf Oil, Potassium Sorbate, Tocopherol (Vitamin E). Limonene* \u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e* Occurs naturally in essential oils\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52880804413767,"sku":null,"price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-sea-mineral-scrub-250g-1052276.webp?v=1765078814"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/kehakoorija.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}